This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3404

This plugin uses Ajax Google Translator ("http://ajax.googleapis.com/&quot;)

Description:
This plugin allows you to translate text using the google online translator.
You can translate as single words and whole blocks using visual-mode.

Note: 
With a large number of text program can take some time

Depending:
1) Ruby                  (Ubuntu: sudo apt-get install ruby)
2) Ruby gem json (Ubuntu: sudo gem install json) only for 1.2 versions

Use:
:Translate Hello World

You can use plugin fork http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3545
he uses gem google-translate
